metadata.name: HARBINGER
metadata.description:
I'm the harbinger, I'll show you what's to come.
The path of all of us is predetermined,
however, fortune favors the prepared.
So better pay attention to my signs...


[ HARBINGER ] is a purely digitally created and 1/1 artwork of which there is no physical original ■ My paintings are built in multiple and overlapping layers on a wide range of colors, patterns, sometimes geometric symbols and signs, which then through light and shadow, create their own special atmosphere ■ Each piece is signed by me and you are guaranteed to buy an individual piece of which there will be no further copy ■ Technical data: File format PNG ■ Size: 4000 x 4000 px (100 dpi) ■ File Size: 28.81 MB
